      <title>TGI Friday 寻找买家，面临债券销售障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/tgi-friday-s-hunts-for-buyer-faces-hurdle-tied-to-bond-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TGI Friday’s Inc. 的一名律师周一表示，该公司正在与潜在买家进行洽谈，并透露，由于失去了对用于担保 2017 年出售的 3.75 亿美元债券的资产的控制权，该公司的收入遭受了“重大”打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/tgi-friday-s-hunts-for-buyer-faces-hurdle-tied-to-bond-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 20:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
